author: ate
msg: Dropping  unused interface methods and their related implementation methods (and also never have been used since their definition back in early 2004).
These methods concerned creating/accessing PortletWindows/PortletEntites specifically *per user*, which we never did or do within Jetspeed.
PortletWindow *state* is by itself already scoped to a user and a PortletEntity its *preferences* are scoped to a user as well, but never the PortletWindow or PortletEntity itself.
